{
  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view captures a vibrant sunset over a coastal landscape. The sky is ablaze with fiery hues of orange and red, transitioning to a softer lavender near the horizon. Wispy contrails from airplanes streak across the sky, adding dynamic lines to the colorful backdrop. Below, a calm body of water reflects some of the sky's warm tones. A distant cityscape is visible along the shoreline, punctuated by a prominent bridge. Small boats are scattered on the water, and the land appears as a dark, silhouetted mass against the brilliant sky. The overall scene evokes a sense of tranquility and awe.",
